title: Justice League - The Flashpoint Paradox DVDRip 2013.flv
description:
Justice League - The Flashpoint Paradox DVDRip 2013.flv

Plot

After stopping a plot by Captain Cold, led by Professor Zoom , to destroy Central City, Flash runs back in time to save his mothers' life. He awakens in a timeline vastly different from the original. Citizen Cold is now the hero of Central City, his Mother is alive, his Father has died of a heart attack and the Justice League does not exist.

Meanwhile in Gotham City a now more violent Batman , who uses guns and lethal force, catches a criminal known as Yo-Yo and demands to know where Joker is. Batman throws Yo-Yo off the building but she is caught by Cyborg, who is now a government agent, before she hits the ground. Batman, Cyborg and a few other heroes via hologram discuss the situation in Europe. Aquaman and the Atlanteans have sunk most of Western Europe apart from Great Britain which was conquered by the Amazons and Christened 'New Themyscira'.

Barry drives to Wayne Manor and enters the Batcave where Batman attacks him. The Batman of this Universe is revealed to be Thomas Wayne , Bruce Wayne's Father and that Bruce had died instead of his parents. Barry tries to retrieve his costume from his ring but finds Professors Zoom's instead causing Barry to think Zoom is the one responsible for this change in reality. After explaining to Batman about the original timeline and that Bruce was Batman there, they decide to recreate the events which gave Barry his powers. However, the first attempt leaves his badly burned and injured.
